 275:Core/Src/port.c ****     /* Start the first task.  This also clears the bit that indicates the FPU is
 276:Core/Src/port.c ****      * in use in case the FPU was used before the scheduler was started - which
ARM GAS  /tmp/cc8ky6Wn.s 			page 7


 277:Core/Src/port.c ****      * would otherwise result in the unnecessary leaving of space in the SVC stack
